{"Id":834595,"Title":"萱妹痛兄而殒作诀妹辞","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"郑孝胥","Context":"如欲有云，不知何言。中心冥顽，孰为心酸。我有女弟，曰嫔于陈。孝恭无间，族姻归仁。天祻吾门，两兄继捐。子不胜丧，从之九泉。嗟我与子，名为弟昆。少小相依，长而遂分。此分非他，子亡我存。各有恨泪，流为黄泉。往者万古，来者亿年。尔我甚殊，倏忽其间。手足奚亲？萍梗奚缘？我寻子形，柷若梦残。兀然惊疑，匪醉而颠。嗟我与子，名为弟昆。曾谓弟昆，不如路人。子为枯骸，我为游魂。从此长绝，理无复全。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"6d7440209bcb37754066999ad7a273fc","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5221472,"Sentence":"手足奚亲？","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shǒu zú xī qīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":12,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221473,"Sentence":"萍梗奚缘？","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"pǐng gěng xī yuán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":13,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221460,"Sentence":"如欲有云，不知何言。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rú yù yǒu yún ，bú zhī hé yán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221461,"Sentence":"中心冥顽，孰为心酸。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhōng xīn mǐng wán ，shú wéi xīn suān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221462,"Sentence":"我有女弟，曰嫔于陈。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ yǒu nǚ dì ，yuē pǐn yú chén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221463,"Sentence":"孝恭无间，族姻归仁。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiào gōng mó jiān ，zú yīn guī rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221464,"Sentence":"天祻吾门，两兄继捐。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tiān gù wú mén ，liǎng xiōng jì juān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221465,"Sentence":"子不胜丧，从之九泉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi bú shēng sāng ，cóng zhī jiu quán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5221466,"Sentence":"嗟我与子，名为弟昆。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jiē wǒ yú zi ，mǐng wéi dì kūn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":52